-- Grafana DB Connection Base is +00:00
-- therefore, to Presented a HOUR, use +offset 
SELECT date_format(  adddate(START_TIME, interval 9 hour), "%H:%i:%s") as T
FROM palmdb.sf_query_history
ORDER BY START_TIME DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT date_format(START_TIME, "%m-%d") AS D
FROM palmdb.sf_query_history
ORDER BY START_TIME DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT count(*) as "-10min"
from palmdb.sf_query_history
WHERE start_time >= adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -10 minute )

SELECT count(*) as "-20min"
from palmdb.sf_query_history
WHERE start_time >= adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -20 minute )
  and start_time < adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -10 minute )

SELECT count(*) as "-30min"
from palmdb.sf_query_history
WHERE start_time >= adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -30 minute )
  and start_time < adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -20 minute )

SELECT count(*) as "-40min"
from palmdb.sf_query_history
WHERE start_time >= adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -40 minute )
    and start_time < adddate( timestamp( now() ), interval -30 minute )

select 
	start_time,
	CNWH_DQM as WH_DQM,
	CNWH_LOAD as WH_LOAD,
	CNWH_DEV as WH_DEV,
	CNWH_PRD	as WH_PRD
from (
	select
		start_TIME,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_DEV_DQM_TEST' then CLUSTER_NUMBER
			else 0
			end CNWH_DQM,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_PRD_LOAD_XS' then CLUSTER_NUMBER
			else 0
			end CNWH_LOAD,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_DEV_XS' then CLUSTER_NUMBER
			else 0
			end CNWH_DEV,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_PRD_XS' then CLUSTER_NUMBER
			else 0
			end CNWH_PRD
	from palmdb.sf_query_history sqh
) result
-- group by START_TIME
order by START_TIME desc
limit 40000

select 
	start_time,
  sum(ALLUSERS)	as ALLUSERS,
	sum(OPSUSER) as OPSUSER,
	sum(DQMADMIN)	as DQM,
	sum(INSYSTEM)	as SYSTEMS,
	sum(DEVELOPER)	as DEVS,
	sum(MSTR) 		as MSTRS
from (
	select
		START_TIME,
		case when USER_NAME = 'DQMADMIN' then 1
			else 0
			end DQMADMIN,
		case when USER_NAME = 'SYSTEM'  then 1
			when USER_NAME = 'PALMADMIN' then 1
			when USER_NAME = 'CDC_PRD' then 1
			when USER_NAME = 'WEB_EXA_PRD' then 1
			else 0
			end INSYSTEM,
		case when USER_NAME = 'PRD_DEVELOPER1' then 1
			when USER_NAME = 'DEV_DEVELOPER1' then 1
			else 0
			end DEVELOPER,
		case when USER_NAME = 'MSTR_PRD' then 1
			else 0
			end MSTR,
		case when USER_NAME like 'Z%' then 1
		  when USER_NAME like 'TS%' then 1
		  else 0
			end OPSUSER,
		case when USER_NAME <> 'MSTR_PRD'
		  and USER_NAME <> 'SYSTEM'
			and USER_NAME <> 'PRD_DEVELOPER1' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'DEV_DEVELOPER1' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'DQMADMIN'
			and USER_NAME <> 'PALMADMIN' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'CDC_PRD' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'WEB_EXA_PRD' 
			and USER_NAME NOT LIKE 'Z%'
			and USER_NAME NOT LIKE 'TS%'
			then 1
			else 0
			end ALLUSERS
	from palmdb.sf_query_history sqh
) result
group by START_TIME
order by START_TIME desc
limit 30000

select 
	start_time,
  sum(WH_X)	as WH_X,
	sum(WH_DQM) as WH_DQM,
	sum(WH_LOAD)	as WH_LOAD,
	sum(WH_DEV)	as WH_DEV,
	sum(WH_PRD)	as WH_PRD
from (
	select
		START_TIME,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_DEV_DQM_TEST' then 1
			else 0
			end WH_DQM,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_PRD_XS'  then 1
			when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_PRD_MSTR' then 1
			else 0
			end WH_PRD,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_DEV_XS' then 1
			else 0
			end WH_DEV,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME = 'WH_PRD_LOAD_XS' then 1
			else 0
			end WH_LOAD,
		case when WAREHOUSE_NAME <> 'WH_PRD_LOAD_XS'
		  and WAREHOUSE_NAME <> 'WH_DEV_XS'
			and WAREHOUSE_NAME <> 'WH_PRD_MSTR' 
			and WAREHOUSE_NAME <> 'WH_PRD_XS' 
			and WAREHOUSE_NAME <> 'WH_DEV_DQM_TEST'
			then 1
			else 0
			end WH_X
	from palmdb.sf_query_history sqh
) result
group by START_TIME
order by START_TIME desc
limit 30000

select 
	start_time,
  sum(ALLUSERS)	/1000 as ALLUSERS,
	sum(OPSUSER) /1000 as OPSUSER,
	sum(DQMADMIN)	/1000 as DQM,
	sum(INSYSTEM)	/1000 as SYSTEMS,
	sum(DEVELOPER) /1000 	as DEVS,
	sum(MSTR) /1000 as MSTRS
from (
	select
		START_TIME,
		case when USER_NAME = 'DQMADMIN' then EXECUTION_TIME
			else 0
			end DQMADMIN,
		case when USER_NAME = 'SYSTEM'  then EXECUTION_TIME
			when USER_NAME = 'PALMADMIN' then EXECUTION_TIME
			when USER_NAME = 'CDC_PRD' then EXECUTION_TIME
			when USER_NAME = 'WEB_EXA_PRD' then EXECUTION_TIME
			else 0
			end INSYSTEM,
		case when USER_NAME = 'PRD_DEVELOPER1' then EXECUTION_TIME
			when USER_NAME = 'DEV_DEVELOPER1' then EXECUTION_TIME
			else 0
			end DEVELOPER,
		case when USER_NAME = 'MSTR_PRD' then EXECUTION_TIME
			else 0
			end MSTR,
		case when USER_NAME like 'Z%' then EXECUTION_TIME
		  when USER_NAME like 'TS%' then EXECUTION_TIME
		  else 0
			end OPSUSER,
		case when USER_NAME <> 'MSTR_PRD'
		  and USER_NAME <> 'SYSTEM'
			and USER_NAME <> 'PRD_DEVELOPER1' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'DEV_DEVELOPER1' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'DQMADMIN'
			and USER_NAME <> 'PALMADMIN' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'CDC_PRD' 
			and USER_NAME <> 'WEB_EXA_PRD' 
			and USER_NAME NOT LIKE 'Z%'
			and USER_NAME NOT LIKE 'TS%'
			then EXECUTION_TIME
			else 0
			end ALLUSERS
	from palmdb.sf_query_history sqh
) result
group by START_TIME
order by START_TIME desc
limit 30000
